Class RandomGenerator_Determined

  • java.lang.Object
    • nsp.impl.random.RandomGenerator_Determined

    public class RandomGenerator_Determined
extends java.lang.Object
implements RandomGenerator, java.lang.Cloneable
    Number generator that implements the RandomGenerator interface, but returns deterministic values. Useful for debugging (i.e. no stochasticity).
